  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Released 12/30/2016 5:25 PM UTC 11:25 AM CT</p><p>This is a minor update to address bugs and add minor features.</p><h3 id=\"id-1.9.1-CreditCardQuickSwipe\">Credit Card Quick Swipe</h3><p>The legacy &quot;quick swipe&quot; field for processing credit cards using the IDTECH SREDKey or M130 device could\u00a0get &quot;stuck&quot; on the loading indicator if you had multiple Credit Card payment methods enabled on a VCT. This is fixed, and having multiple credit card payment methods enabled on a VCT should no longer\u00a0cause any problems.</p>",
